::Perndabot::

Perndabot stops at the edge of the forest, nodding. The Cybertronian Fire was 
a good distance away, he just hoped the Maximals could keep up with 
BrightBlade long enough for her to bring over some Maximals.

"I'm always ready," he says, leaning against a tree, which bends slightly at 
his weight.
